{"content":{"raw":"[section label=\"desktop\" bg=\"1620\" bg_overlay=\"rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96)\" padding=\"0px\"]\n\n[row style=\"collapse\" width=\"full-width\" h_align=\"center\"]\n\n[col span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_banner height=\"500px\" bg=\"2151\" bg_size=\"original\" bg_pos=\"56% 22%\" parallax=\"2\"]\n\n[text_box width=\"100\" scale=\"30\" padding=\"5px 0px 9px 0px\" position_x=\"50\" position_y=\"100\" bg=\"rgba(81, 190, 137, 0.31)\"]\n\n<h1><a href=\"#contact1\"><span style=\"font-size: 130%;\">Ongoing Monthly SEO Campaign<\/span><\/a><\/h1>\n\n[\/text_box]\n\n[\/ux_banner]\n\n[\/col]\n\n[\/row]\n[row h_align=\"center\"]\n\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"8\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"1494\" img_width=\"46\" pos=\"center\" font_size=\"small\"]\n\n<h3>KEYWORD RESEARCH<\/h3>\n<p>Finding relevant keywords and search volume for your specific niche, collection official search volume information from Google Adwords and other web tools.<\/p>\n\n[\/featured_box]\n\n[\/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"8\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"1496\" img_width=\"46\" pos=\"center\" font_size=\"small\"]\n\n<h3>COMPETITOR RESEARCH<\/h3>\n<p>Identifying &amp; segmenting top competition in the immediate &amp; non immediate niche. Competitor marketing strategy breakdown and website stats such as number of visits, traffic sources, user GEO location, top pages etc.<\/p>\n\n[\/featured_box]\n\n[\/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"8\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"1495\" img_width=\"46\" pos=\"center\" font_size=\"small\"]\n\n<h3>WEBSITE SECURITY<\/h3>\n<p>Before initiating any online marketing campaign we have to make sure that all the code and server infrastructure is secure for all daily tasks, preventing vulnerabilities, malware, hacking, DDos attacks, and downtime.<\/p>\n\n[\/featured_box]\n\n[\/col]\n\n[\/row]\n[gap height=\"37px\"]\n\n[row h_align=\"center\"]\n\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"8\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"1493\" img_width=\"46\" pos=\"center\" font_size=\"small\"]\n\n<h3>CONTENT STRATEGY<\/h3>\n<p>Planing a long term content strategy to get higher search rankings and more relevant search terms as part of the On-page SEO plan.<\/p>\n\n[\/featured_box]\n\n[\/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"8\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"1491\" img_width=\"46\" pos=\"center\" font_size=\"small\"]\n\n<h3>TRACKING &amp; ANALYTICS<\/h3>\n<p>Installing Google tracking tools (Google analytics, Google search Console), Creating custom events and user flow analysis to improve conversion and user insights.<\/p>\n\n[\/featured_box]\n\n[\/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"8\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"1492\" img_width=\"46\" pos=\"center\" font_size=\"small\"]\n\n<h3>SITE SPEED<\/h3>\n<p>Checking &amp; Improving the current website and server structure in order to improve site speed, reduce server load, improve user experience and have a positive effect on search engine crawlability and rankings.<\/p>\n\n[\/featured_box]\n\n[\/col]\n\n[\/row]\n[row]\n\n[col span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[divider align=\"center\"]\n\n[title style=\"center\" text=\"An ongoing SEO campaign can start after finalizing the initial SEO strategy.\" size=\"115\"]\n\n[tabgroup title=\"SEO CAMPAIGN BREAKEDOWN\" style=\"pills\" type=\"vertical\" nav_size=\"xlarge\"]\n\n[tab title=\"ONPAGE SEO\"]\n\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">On-page SEO: all site SEO overview.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Content optimization: Tweaking and improving existing content.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Mobile device optimization: Multi device compatibility for optimal user experience.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Keyword tracking: Track &amp; measure the growth of organic traffic constantly.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Traffic analysis: Breakdown the user behavior and optimize accordingly.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Code optimization: Optimize the code according to Google's official SEO guidelines.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">CRO: conversion optimization<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Social profiles: creation &amp; integration of all the social platforms relevant for your business.<\/p>\n<p>After 3 months we reevaluate the campaign and optimize accordingly.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n[\/tab]\n[tab title=\"Content writing\"]\n\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Write and publish SEO content your website to rank on new keywords and rank higher on existing keywords.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Provide your audience useful &amp; relevant information so your readers become customers and also share your content with their friends and networks.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Brand your business as a market leader, knowledge base and a thought provider in your industry.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n[\/tab]\n[tab title=\"PR And Outreach\"]\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>Public relations and outreach services to leading online news sites and other niche specific sites.<\/p>\n<p>Spread out your business service or product on a high scale level with mass news sites that offer high daily impressions.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n[\/tab]\n[tab title=\"Local SEO\"]\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>Optimize your site to rank higher on local searches on Google Business\/Google maps, both on mobile and desktop.<\/p>\n<p>Get more calls, and navigation to your business address every day.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n[\/tab]\n[tab title=\"Guest post services\"]\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>Connect to other online business partners, collaborate and share audiences with their websites by publishing your content on other websites.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n[\/tab]\n\n[\/tabgroup]\n\n[\/col]\n\n[\/row]\n[scroll_to title=\"contact us 1\" link=\"contact1\" bullet=\"false\"]\n\n[block id=\"2627\"]\n\n\n[\/section]","rendered":"\t<section class=\"section\" id=\"section_60247501\">\n\t\t<div class=\"bg section-bg fill bg-fill bg-loaded \" >\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<div class=\"section-bg-overlay absolute fill\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"section-content relative\">\n\t