n<div class=\"container section-title-container\" ><h3 class=\"section-title section-title-center\"><b><\/b><span class=\"section-title-main\" style=\"font-size:115%;\">An ongoing SEO campaign can start after finalizing the initial SEO strategy.<\/span><b><\/b><\/h3><\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"tabbed-content\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"uppercase text-left\">SEO CAMPAIGN BREAKEDOWN<\/h4>\n\t\t\t<ul class=\"nav nav-pills nav-vertical nav-uppercase nav-size-xlarge nav-left\"><li class=\"tab active has-icon\"><a href=\"#tab_onpage-seo\"><span>ONPAGE SEO<\/span><\/a><\/li>\n<li class=\"tab has-icon\"><a href=\"#tab_content-writing\"><span>Content writing<\/span><\/a><\/li>\n<li class=\"tab has-icon\"><a href=\"#tab_pr-and-outreach\"><span>PR And Outreach<\/span><\/a><\/li>\n<li class=\"tab has-icon\"><a href=\"#tab_local-seo\"><span>Local SEO<\/span><\/a><\/li>\n<li class=\"tab has-icon\"><a href=\"#tab_guest-post-services\"><span>Guest post services<\/span><\/a><\/li><\/ul><div class=\"tab-panels\"><div class=\"panel active entry-content\" id=\"tab_onpage-seo\">\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">On-page SEO: all site SEO overview.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Content optimization: Tweaking and improving existing content.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Mobile device optimization: Multi device compatibility for optimal user experience.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Keyword tracking: Track &amp; measure the growth of organic traffic constantly.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Traffic analysis: Breakdown the user behavior and optimize accordingly.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Code optimization: Optimize the code according to Google&#8217;s official SEO guidelines.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">CRO: conversion optimization<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Social profiles: creation &amp; integration of all the social platforms relevant for your business.<\/p>\n<p>After 3 months we reevaluate the campaign and optimize accordingly.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"panel entry-content\" id=\"tab_content-writing\">\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Write and publish SEO content your website to rank on new keywords and rank higher on existing keywords.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Provide your audience useful &amp; relevant information so your readers become customers and also share your content with their friends and networks.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Brand your business as a market leader, knowledge base and a thought provider in your industry.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"panel entry-content\" id=\"tab_pr-and-outreach\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Public relations and outreach services to leading online news sites and other niche specific sites.<\/p>\n<p>Spread out your business service or product on a high scale level with mass news sites that offer high daily impressions.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"panel entry-content\" id=\"tab_local-seo\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Optimize your site to rank higher on local searches on Google Business\/Google maps, both on mobile and desktop.<\/p>\n<p>Get more calls, and navigation to your business address every day.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"panel entry-content\" id=\"tab_guest-post-services\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Connect to other online business partners, collaborate and share audiences with their websites by publishing your content on other websites.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n<span class=\"scroll-to\" data-label=\"Scroll to: #contact1\" data-bullet=\"false\" data-link=\"#contact1\" data-title=\"contact us 1\"><a name=\"contact1\"><\/a><\/span>\n<div class=\"block-edit-link\" data-title=\"Edit Block: Get In Touch\"   data-backend=\"https:\/\/www.seokru.com\/wp-admin\/post.php?post=2627&#038;action=edit\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.seokru.com\/wp-admin\/post.php?post=1524&#038;action=edit&#038;app=uxbuilder&#038;t